      • createNew

        @NonNull
public static AccountKey createNew(@NonNull
                                            android.net.Uri fogReportUri,
                                            @NonNull
                                            String fogReportId,
                                            @NonNull
                                            byte[] fogAuthoritySpki)
                                     throws InvalidUriException
        Create an AccountKey object from auto-generated account keys and fog info. SecureRandom is used to generate entropy.
        Parameters:
        fogReportUri - fog report service url.
        fogAuthoritySpki - fog authority public key a byte array, provided by the fog operator
        fogReportId - The fog report server may serve multiple reports, this id disambiguates which one to use when sending to this account
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if method parameters are invalid
        InvalidUriException

public static AccountKey fromMnemonicPhrase(@NonNull

                                                     @NonNull
                                                     String fogReportId,
                                                     @NonNull

                                              throws BadMnemonicException,
                                                     InvalidUriException
        Derives the nth AccountKey from a mnemonic
        Parameters:
        fogReportUri - fog report service url.
        fogAuthoritySpki - fog authority public key a byte array, provided by the fog operator.
        fogReportId - The fog report server may serve multiple reports, this id. disambiguates which one to use when sending to this account.
        mnemonicPhrase - is used as a recovery phrase to derive an AccountKey.
        accountIndex - account index to derive.
        Throws:
        BadMnemonicException
        InvalidUriException

        Parameters:
        fogReportUri - fog report service url.
        fogAuthoritySpki - fog authority public key a byte array, provided by the fog operator.
        fogReportId - The fog report server may serve multiple reports, this id. disambiguates which one to use when sending to this account.
        bip39Entropy - mnemonic entropy, see Mnemonics.bip39EntropyFromMnemonic(java.lang.String).
